Text.SourceString: I don't know what your angle is, but I've got nothing for you.
Text.LocalizedString: I don't know what your angle is, but I've got nothing for you.

Text.SourceString: Best you remember that.
Text.LocalizedString: Best you remember that.

Text.SourceString: Your kind has a reputation, and it's not good.
Text.LocalizedString: Your kind has a reputation, and it's not good.

Text.SourceString: You're invading my personal space. Step back!
Text.LocalizedString: You're invading my personal space. Step back!

Text.SourceString: You're no savior. I don't buy it.//The King might place his faith in you, but I'm here to be the voice of caution for him.
Text.LocalizedString: You're no savior. I don't buy it.//The King might place his faith in you, but I'm here to be the voice of caution for him.

Text.SourceString: I'm devoted to fulfilling the King's commands. Even if he orders me to march into a battle we're destined to lose.//<portrait=annoyed>So don't confuse my presence with acceptance, land-dweller.
Text.LocalizedString: I'm devoted to fulfilling the King's commands. Even if he orders me to march into a battle we're destined to lose.//<portrait=annoyed>So don't confuse my presence with acceptance, land-dweller.

Text.SourceString: As the lead guard of the kingdom, my duty is to ensure the safety and security of all who reside within our realm.
Text.LocalizedString: As the lead guard of the kingdom, my duty is to ensure the safety and security of all who reside within our realm.

Text.SourceString: If this arrangement puts that at risk, I <Italic>will</> step in.
Text.LocalizedString: If this arrangement puts that at risk, I <Italic>will</> step in.

Text.SourceString: I've dealt with enough land-dwellers in my existence, and let me tell you, most of them have caused nothing but trouble.
Text.LocalizedString: I've dealt with enough land-dwellers in my existence, and let me tell you, most of them have caused nothing but trouble.

Text.SourceString: I'm watching your every move.
Text.LocalizedString: I'm watching your every move.

Text.SourceString: If I were in your shoes, I'd stop wasting time and start doing something useful, instead of wandering around aimlessly, chattering away like a fool.
Text.LocalizedString: If I were in your shoes, I'd stop wasting time and start doing something useful, instead of wandering around aimlessly, chattering away like a fool.

Text.SourceString: The idea of going up to the shore has never piqued my interest.//It truly baffles me why you're so desperate to be here... What's so captivating about this place, huh?
Text.LocalizedString: The idea of going up to the shore has never piqued my interest.//It truly baffles me why you're so desperate to be here... What's so captivating about this place, huh?

Text.SourceString: Make sure you don't run out of oxygen, because the last thing I need is the inconvenience of rescuing you from your own recklessness.
Text.LocalizedString: Make sure you don't run out of oxygen, because the last thing I need is the inconvenience of rescuing you from your own recklessness.

Text.SourceString: What is it that you do up at the shore?
Text.LocalizedString: What is it that you do up at the shore?

Text.SourceString: You don't strike me as guard material, I must say.
Text.LocalizedString: You don't strike me as guard material, I must say.

Text.SourceString: It's my duty to maintain order amidst the chaos...to keep a watchful eye on <NPCName>Princess Miranjani</>'s escapades.
Text.LocalizedString: It's my duty to maintain order amidst the chaos...to keep a watchful eye on <NPCName>Princess Miranjani</>'s escapades.

Text.SourceString: Under the King's rule, our realm thrives, and his strategic prowess keeps our enemies at bay.
Text.LocalizedString: Under the King's rule, our realm thrives, and his strategic prowess keeps our enemies at bay.

Text.SourceString: You're a good friend, <PlayerName>$Player</>.//Thank you for always being there for me.
Text.LocalizedString: You're a good friend, <PlayerName>$Player</>.//Thank you for always being there for me.

Text.SourceString: The Deep is not something we meddle with...it's a dangerous place to be.//I must admit, it's impressive that you secured that part of the ocean.
Text.LocalizedString: The Deep is not something we meddle with...it's a dangerous place to be.//I must admit, it's impressive that you secured that part of the ocean.

Text.SourceString: You have played a role in keeping our Kingdom safe.//I extend my respect to you.
Text.LocalizedString: You have played a role in keeping our Kingdom safe.//I extend my respect to you.

Text.SourceString: Every day, I stand as a steadfast guardian, shielding our kingdom from external dangers...and internal disturbances.
Text.LocalizedString: Every day, I stand as a steadfast guardian, shielding our kingdom from external dangers...and internal disturbances.

Text.SourceString: You can wander around all you want, just remember to tread lightly and stay within your boundaries.
Text.LocalizedString: You can wander around all you want, just remember to tread lightly and stay within your boundaries.

Text.SourceString: Don't go poking your nose where it doesn't belong.
Text.LocalizedString: Don't go poking your nose where it doesn't belong.

Text.SourceString: I've had my fill of your constant chatter.
Text.LocalizedString: I've had my fill of your constant chatter.

Text.SourceString: You're blocking my path. Excuse me.
Text.LocalizedString: You're blocking my path. Excuse me.

Text.SourceString: My spear is off-limits, and it's in your best interest to steer clear.
Text.LocalizedString: My spear is off-limits, and it's in your best interest to steer clear.

Text.SourceString: We, merfolk, have no use for excessive layers like you land-dwellers.//We wear only what we need, embracing the freedom of our aquatic domain.
Text.LocalizedString: We, merfolk, have no use for excessive layers like you land-dwellers.//We wear only what we need, embracing the freedom of our aquatic domain.

Text.SourceString: I don't have the time for a chat today.//I have important matters to attend.
Text.LocalizedString: I don't have the time for a chat today.//I have important matters to attend.

Text.SourceString: I have nothing to say to you.
Text.LocalizedString: I have nothing to say to you.

Text.SourceString: You're blocking my path. Excuse me.
Text.LocalizedString: You're blocking my path. Excuse me.

Text.SourceString: Didn't really think we'd find Poseidon in the kingdom, to be honest.
Text.LocalizedString: Didn't really think we'd find Poseidon in the kingdom, to be honest.

Text.SourceString: Poseidon always did have a habit of disappearing. I just never imagined he wouldn't come back home.
Text.LocalizedString: Poseidon always did have a habit of disappearing. I just never imagined he wouldn't come back home.

Text.SourceString: Thanks for helping me look for my lobster, I guess. Didn't expect anyone to bother.
Text.LocalizedString: Thanks for helping me look for my lobster, I guess. Didn't expect anyone to bother.

Text.SourceString: Let's just say I'm not holding my breath on this search.
Text.LocalizedString: Let's just say I'm not holding my breath on this search.

Text.SourceString: I knew it'd be a long shot. Poseidon's never been easy to track.
Text.LocalizedString: I knew it'd be a long shot. Poseidon's never been easy to track.

Text.SourceString: Didn't think I'd enjoy the company, but it's not so bad.
Text.LocalizedString: Didn't think I'd enjoy the company, but it's not so bad.

Text.SourceString: Thanks for sticking around. Not many would.
Text.LocalizedString: Thanks for sticking around. Not many would.

Text.SourceString: Oh, <PlayerName>$Player</>, it's you. Always a pleasant surprise to bump into you.
Text.LocalizedString: Oh, <PlayerName>$Player</>, it's you. Always a pleasant surprise to bump into you.

Text.SourceString: You know, you have a way of making this place more interesting.
Text.LocalizedString: You know, you have a way of making this place more interesting.

Text.SourceString: There's that smile I've been thinking about.
Text.LocalizedString: There's that smile I've been thinking about.

Text.SourceString: Was hoping I'd run into you. Guess today's my lucky day.
Text.LocalizedString: Was hoping I'd run into you. Guess today's my lucky day.

Text.SourceString: It's nice to see a pretty face around, especially when it's yours.
Text.LocalizedString: It's nice to see a pretty face around, especially when it's yours.

Text.SourceString: Just when I thought I couldn’t love you more, there you go smiling at me like that.
Text.LocalizedString: Just when I thought I couldn’t love you more, there you go smiling at me like that.

Text.SourceString: Seeing Poseidon happy like that...it's a lot to take in.//<portrait=happy>I didn't expect to feel this way, but I'm glad he's safe.
Text.LocalizedString: Seeing Poseidon happy like that...it's a lot to take in.//<portrait=happy>I didn't expect to feel this way, but I'm glad he's safe.

Text.SourceString: Macy seems nice. Good that Pose--, um, Stephen found someone like her.
Text.LocalizedString: Macy seems nice. Good that Pose--, um, Stephen found someone like her.

Text.SourceString: Never thought I'd be playing volleyball of all things.
Text.LocalizedString: Never thought I'd be playing volleyball of all things.

Text.SourceString: Thanks for teaching me volleyball, even if I'm not the best student.//<portrait=blushing>You're very patient, which is one of the things I like the most about you.
Text.LocalizedString: Thanks for teaching me volleyball, even if I'm not the best student.//<portrait=blushing>You're very patient, which is one of the things I like the most about you.

Text.SourceString: This volleyball thing is...actually kind of fun. We need to do that again soon.
Text.LocalizedString: This volleyball thing is...actually kind of fun. We need to do that again soon.

Text.SourceString: Life's strange. You look for a lost pet, end up playing volleyball.
Text.LocalizedString: Life's strange. You look for a lost pet, end up playing volleyball.

Text.SourceString: Maybe I should lighten up a bit. Maybe.
Text.LocalizedString: Maybe I should lighten up a bit. Maybe.

Text.SourceString: I've been thinking about Poseidon. He's better off, I guess.
Text.LocalizedString: I've been thinking about Poseidon. He's better off, I guess.

Text.SourceString: I'm not one for people, but there's something about you that I just can't resist.
Text.LocalizedString: I'm not one for people, but there's something about you that I just can't resist.

Text.SourceString: I never thought I'd say this, but I've had a crush on you for a while now.
Text.LocalizedString: I never thought I'd say this, but I've had a crush on you for a while now.

Text.SourceString: It's strange for me to admit, but I find myself drawn to you in a way I can't quite explain. You've been on my mind more than I care to admit.
Text.LocalizedString: It's strange for me to admit, but I find myself drawn to you in a way I can't quite explain. You've been on my mind more than I care to admit.

Text.SourceString: You're the only person who's ever made me reconsider my stance on keeping to myself.//Maybe they're right, when you know, you know.
Text.LocalizedString: You're the only person who's ever made me reconsider my stance on keeping to myself.//Maybe they're right, when you know, you know.

Text.SourceString: You're a great friend, <PlayerName>$Player</>. I'm really thankful you're a part of my life.
Text.LocalizedString: You're a great friend, <PlayerName>$Player</>. I'm really thankful you're a part of my life.

Text.SourceString: The beach was interesting. On land, everything feels so immediate, so tangible.
Text.LocalizedString: The beach was interesting. On land, everything feels so immediate, so tangible.

Text.SourceString: That trip to the shore...it's left an impression on me. The land has its own kind of beauty, doesn't it?
Text.LocalizedString: That trip to the shore...it's left an impression on me. The land has its own kind of beauty, doesn't it?

Text.SourceString: Just finished a chapter on ancient military tactics. Fascinating stuff.
Text.LocalizedString: Just finished a chapter on ancient military tactics. Fascinating stuff.

Text.SourceString: I don't need much. Just the essentials.
Text.LocalizedString: I don't need much. Just the essentials.

Text.SourceString: The less I have, the fewer distractions I face.
Text.LocalizedString: The less I have, the fewer distractions I face.

Text.SourceString: Nothing clears the mind like a long swim.
Text.LocalizedString: Nothing clears the mind like a long swim.

Text.SourceString: Sometimes, I just need to be alone with my thoughts.
Text.LocalizedString: Sometimes, I just need to be alone with my thoughts.

Text.SourceString: There's comfort in solitude, a peace you can't find in crowds.
Text.LocalizedString: There's comfort in solitude, a peace you can't find in crowds.

Text.SourceString: The ocean has always been my home, my sanctuary.
Text.LocalizedString: The ocean has always been my home, my sanctuary.

Text.SourceString: Concise and clear – that's how information should be presented.//Why write a scroll when a sentence will do?
Text.LocalizedString: Concise and clear – that's how information should be presented.//Why write a scroll when a sentence will do?

Text.SourceString: Why do people enjoy these loud gatherings?
Text.LocalizedString: Why do people enjoy these loud gatherings?

Text.SourceString: I've never been much for desserts, but I have to make an exception for frozen seagrass – that stuff is amazing.
Text.LocalizedString: I've never been much for desserts, but I have to make an exception for frozen seagrass – that stuff is amazing.

Text.SourceString: We need to revise our tactics. The traditional methods aren't enough for the new challenges we face, like the rising number of land dwellers visiting our realm.
Text.LocalizedString: We need to revise our tactics. The traditional methods aren't enough for the new challenges we face, like the rising number of land dwellers visiting our realm.

Text.SourceString: All clear on the western front, but let's not get complacent.
Text.LocalizedString: All clear on the western front, but let's not get complacent.

Text.SourceString: Recent patrols report no immediate threats, but we'll keep our guard up.
Text.LocalizedString: Recent patrols report no immediate threats, but we'll keep our guard up.

Text.SourceString: A good workout is the best start to any day. I can tell you share the same value.
Text.LocalizedString: A good workout is the best start to any day. I can tell you share the same value.

Text.SourceString: My back is very sore. I think I went overboard yesterday with working out.
Text.LocalizedString: My back is very sore. I think I went overboard yesterday with working out.

Text.SourceString: Early morning training is tough, but it sets the right tone for the day.
Text.LocalizedString: Early morning training is tough, but it sets the right tone for the day.

Text.SourceString: Cooked too much last night, looks like it's kelp salad for me for the next few days.
Text.LocalizedString: Cooked too much last night, looks like it's kelp salad for me for the next few days.

Text.SourceString: Olan always brings the best kelp to the palace, and he's generous enough to share with us guards. I appreciate that about him.
Text.LocalizedString: Olan always brings the best kelp to the palace, and he's generous enough to share with us guards. I appreciate that about him.

Text.SourceString: I don't have any favorite food, but I must admit, reef burgers are pretty decent.
Text.LocalizedString: I don't have any favorite food, but I must admit, reef burgers are pretty decent.

Text.SourceString: Those drinks from the land, they're surprisingly refreshing.//<portrait=sad>Had my first sip from a bottle found in a sunken ship...but that's not a particularly cheerful story.
Text.LocalizedString: Those drinks from the land, they're surprisingly refreshing.//<portrait=sad>Had my first sip from a bottle found in a sunken ship...but that's not a particularly cheerful story.

Text.SourceString: Being a soldier is all I've ever envisioned for myself.//<portrait=blushing>Serving is in my blood, and maybe a marriage and a small family in the future.
Text.LocalizedString: Being a soldier is all I've ever envisioned for myself.//<portrait=blushing>Serving is in my blood, and maybe a marriage and a small family in the future.

Text.SourceString: I hope for peace, always. But if war calls, it's my duty to respond, no questions asked.
Text.LocalizedString: I hope for peace, always. But if war calls, it's my duty to respond, no questions asked.

Text.SourceString: I've had my share of complaints about <NPCName>Denali</>, that mermaid...ah!//But I can't deny she's good at what she does. Keeps things balanced with <NPCName>Agung</>.
Text.LocalizedString: I've had my share of complaints about <NPCName>Denali</>, that mermaid...ah!//But I can't deny she's good at what she does. Keeps things balanced with <NPCName>Agung</>.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Denali</>'s snapping at the crabs wasn't her finest moment. Her temper needs some work.//We got a formal complaint from the Crab Clan about it.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Denali</>'s snapping at the crabs wasn't her finest moment. Her temper needs some work.//We got a formal complaint from the Crab Clan about it.

Text.SourceString: Sometimes I'm tired of smoothing things over after <NPCName>Denali</> loses it.
Text.LocalizedString: Sometimes I'm tired of smoothing things over after <NPCName>Denali</> loses it.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Denali</>'s temper flares are really starting to drain me. I suggested morning workouts to help her vent some of that energy, but it doesn’t seem to be making much difference.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Denali</>'s temper flares are really starting to drain me. I suggested morning workouts to help her vent some of that energy, but it doesn’t seem to be making much difference.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Agung</> may not always seem focused, what with his shell obsession, but he's dependable and unwaveringly loyal to our cause.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Agung</> may not always seem focused, what with his shell obsession, but he's dependable and unwaveringly loyal to our cause.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Agung</> and his shells, I swear. I witnessed the grand shell avalanche.//Shells rolling everywhere, it was like a chaotic shell parade.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Agung</> and his shells, I swear. I witnessed the grand shell avalanche.//Shells rolling everywhere, it was like a chaotic shell parade.

Text.SourceString: Someone really should talk to <NPCName>Agung</> about those shell piles near his grotto. It's becoming a hazard waiting to happen.
Text.LocalizedString: Someone really should talk to <NPCName>Agung</> about those shell piles near his grotto. It's becoming a hazard waiting to happen.

Text.SourceString: I prefer staying at the barracks; it's where my fellow soldiers are, and it's where I belong.//I wish I had a bigger kitchen, though.
Text.LocalizedString: I prefer staying at the barracks; it's where my fellow soldiers are, and it's where I belong.//I wish I had a bigger kitchen, though.

Text.SourceString: Olan's been kind enough to let me use his kitchen for meal prep when needed. It's generous of him, but I can't help feeling like I'm imposing sometimes.
Text.LocalizedString: Olan's been kind enough to let me use his kitchen for meal prep when needed. It's generous of him, but I can't help feeling like I'm imposing sometimes.

Text.SourceString: The king offers me a place in the palace, long may he reign.//But if I'm there, who would oversee the grounds?
Text.LocalizedString: The king offers me a place in the palace, long may he reign.//But if I'm there, who would oversee the grounds?

Text.SourceString: Have you seen any strange creatures on the surface? I've always wondered what kind of wildlife exists up there.
Text.LocalizedString: Have you seen any strange creatures on the surface? I've always wondered what kind of wildlife exists up there.

Text.SourceString: Hmm, a deer, you say? Interesting.
Text.LocalizedString: Hmm, a deer, you say? Interesting.

Special.SourceString: I once saw a deer while hiking in the forest. It was beautiful!
Special.LocalizedString: I once saw a deer while hiking in the forest. It was beautiful!

Text.SourceString: Birds and squirrels, huh? Sounds peaceful.
Text.LocalizedString: Birds and squirrels, huh? Sounds peaceful.

Special.SourceString: I haven't seen anything too unusual, mostly just birds and squirrels.
Special.LocalizedString: I haven't seen anything too unusual, mostly just birds and squirrels.

Text.SourceString: A raccoon thief? That's quite the story.
Text.LocalizedString: A raccoon thief? That's quite the story.

Special.SourceString: I had a run-in with a raccoon once. It stole my sandwich right out of my hand!
Special.LocalizedString: I had a run-in with a raccoon once. It stole my sandwich right out of my hand!

Text.SourceString: What do you enjoy doing in your free time?
Text.LocalizedString: What do you enjoy doing in your free time?

Text.SourceString: Painting, huh? I can appreciate the beauty of art.//Your creativity must be captivating.
Text.LocalizedString: Painting, huh? I can appreciate the beauty of art.//Your creativity must be captivating.

Special.SourceString: I love painting. I find it really relaxing and a great way to express myself.
Special.LocalizedString: I love painting. I find it really relaxing and a great way to express myself.

Text.SourceString: Maybe you can show me how I can use my hands efficiently.
Text.LocalizedString: Maybe you can show me how I can use my hands efficiently.

Special.SourceString: I like farming. I'm good with my hands.
Special.LocalizedString: I like farming. I'm good with my hands.

Text.SourceString: Playing music, that's something I'd like to learn more about someday.//Maybe you can teach me, and we can create our own melody.
Text.LocalizedString: Playing music, that's something I'd like to learn more about someday.//Maybe you can teach me, and we can create our own melody.

Special.SourceString: I enjoy playing musical instruments. It helps me unwind.
Special.LocalizedString: I enjoy playing musical instruments. It helps me unwind.

Text.SourceString: What are your thoughts on the security of our kingdom?
Text.LocalizedString: What are your thoughts on the security of our kingdom?

Text.SourceString: Additional training, a valid point. We must stay prepared.
Text.LocalizedString: Additional training, a valid point. We must stay prepared.

Special.SourceString: More training for the guards could help.
Special.LocalizedString: More training for the guards could help.

Text.SourceString: Stronger walls, noted. They could provide an added layer of defense.
Text.LocalizedString: Stronger walls, noted. They could provide an added layer of defense.

Text.SourceString: Maybe I should be your personal guard then.
Text.LocalizedString: Maybe I should be your personal guard then.

Special.SourceString: I feel safe here with you.
Special.LocalizedString: I feel safe here with you.

Text.SourceString: You need to be more careful out there. This world can be unforgiving.
Text.LocalizedString: You need to be more careful out there. This world can be unforgiving.

Text.SourceString: I expect you to report back to me immediately if anything feels off.
Text.LocalizedString: I expect you to report back to me immediately if anything feels off.

Text.SourceString: Stay close to me. I won't have you wandering too far.
Text.LocalizedString: Stay close to me. I won't have you wandering too far.

Text.SourceString: I don't want you getting hurt. Stick by my side.
Text.LocalizedString: I don't want you getting hurt. Stick by my side.

Text.SourceString: I'm responsible for your safety. Don't forget that.
Text.LocalizedString: I'm responsible for your safety. Don't forget that.

Text.SourceString: You're under my protection. That means you follow my rules.
Text.LocalizedString: You're under my protection. That means you follow my rules.

Text.SourceString: I'll do whatever it takes to keep you safe, even if you don't like it.
Text.LocalizedString: I'll do whatever it takes to keep you safe, even if you don't like it.

Text.SourceString: Let's have you back home. It's late.
Text.LocalizedString: Let's have you back home. It's late.

Text.SourceString: Took me a day to assist the wandering turtle back to its cave yesterday.
Text.LocalizedString: Took me a day to assist the wandering turtle back to its cave yesterday.

Text.SourceString: Seeing a family of seahorses in the coral reef reminds me of my own family.
Text.LocalizedString: Seeing a family of seahorses in the coral reef reminds me of my own family.

Text.SourceString: They weren't particularly nurturing, my family...I mean.//I don't know where they were. After I was hatched, I was pretty much on my own.
Text.LocalizedString: They weren't particularly nurturing, my family...I mean.//I don't know where they were. After I was hatched, I was pretty much on my own.

Text.SourceString: Sometimes, I think about what it would have been like to have a different upbringing, one with more guidance and support.
Text.LocalizedString: Sometimes, I think about what it would have been like to have a different upbringing, one with more guidance and support.

Text.SourceString: I guess I've always been a bit of a lone wolf, but I wouldn't have it any other way.//<portrait=sad>So, I decided that if they didn't want me, I didn't want them either.
Text.LocalizedString: I guess I've always been a bit of a lone wolf, but I wouldn't have it any other way.//<portrait=sad>So, I decided that if they didn't want me, I didn't want them either.

Text.SourceString: When I hatched, I didn't have the luxury of a loving family waiting for me. No warm welcomes, no guiding fins.//I was alone in that vast ocean, but it toughened me up real quick.
Text.LocalizedString: When I hatched, I didn't have the luxury of a loving family waiting for me. No warm welcomes, no guiding fins.//I was alone in that vast ocean, but it toughened me up real quick.

Text.SourceString: I guess you could say the sea was my first teacher.
Text.LocalizedString: I guess you could say the sea was my first teacher.

Text.SourceString: The military, they took me in when no one else would. They gave me purpose, a place to belong.
Text.LocalizedString: The military, they took me in when no one else would. They gave me purpose, a place to belong.

Text.SourceString: Sometimes, it's better to create your own family from the bonds you forge along the way.
Text.LocalizedString: Sometimes, it's better to create your own family from the bonds you forge along the way.

Text.SourceString: You're a good friend, <PlayerName>$player</>.//Thank you for always being there for me.
Text.LocalizedString: You're a good friend, <PlayerName>$player</>.//Thank you for always being there for me.

Text.SourceString: I heard a rumor about a potential threat from the deep sea creatures. We need to stay vigilant.//<portrait=blushing>Although, it could also be a conversation about eating giant seagrapes. My understanding of squid language isn't so good. I might have misunderstood.
Text.LocalizedString: I heard a rumor about a potential threat from the deep sea creatures. We need to stay vigilant.//<portrait=blushing>Although, it could also be a conversation about eating giant seagrapes. My understanding of squid language isn't so good. I might have misunderstood.

Text.SourceString: Sometimes, during my patrols, I swim up to the surface to watch the sunset. It's a rare moment of peace.
Text.LocalizedString: Sometimes, during my patrols, I swim up to the surface to watch the sunset. It's a rare moment of peace.

Text.SourceString: You should join me sometime. I'll show you a spot.
Text.LocalizedString: You should join me sometime. I'll show you a spot.

Text.SourceString: I've been practicing a new combat move. Want me to show you later?
Text.LocalizedString: I've been practicing a new combat move. Want me to show you later?

Text.SourceString: I had a chat with <NPCName>Agung</> today. He took a snail from its family again.//<portrait=angry>It turned into a formal complaint. That guy, I swear, he gives me a headache.
Text.LocalizedString: I had a chat with <NPCName>Agung</> today. He took a snail from its family again.//<portrait=angry>It turned into a formal complaint. That guy, I swear, he gives me a headache.

Text.SourceString: Olan offered to teach me a new recipe. I might give it a try.
Text.LocalizedString: Olan offered to teach me a new recipe. I might give it a try.

Text.SourceString: Princess Miranjani, she's a handful, that one. Always sneaking off without a care in the world.
Text.LocalizedString: Princess Miranjani, she's a handful, that one. Always sneaking off without a care in the world.

Text.SourceString: Honestly, you'd think she'd outgrow this habit of hers by now.//But it is my duty to keep the princess safe, and I will make sure of that.
Text.LocalizedString: Honestly, you'd think she'd outgrow this habit of hers by now.//But it is my duty to keep the princess safe, and I will make sure of that.

Text.SourceString: I've noticed that the princess gets along well with <NPCName>Deno</>, so I often assign her to accompany the princess during her engagements.
Text.LocalizedString: I've noticed that the princess gets along well with <NPCName>Deno</>, so I often assign her to accompany the princess during her engagements.

Text.SourceString: I'm aware that I'm not a favorite around here, but I don't care.//My role isn't to win popularity. It's to safeguard the kingdom and its merfolk, and that's precisely what I intend to do.
Text.LocalizedString: I'm aware that I'm not a favorite around here, but I don't care.//My role isn't to win popularity. It's to safeguard the kingdom and its merfolk, and that's precisely what I intend to do.

Text.SourceString: The lighting in this place is far too dim. I asked the owner to brighten it up a bit for Princess Miranjani, but he just laughed it off.//I didn't find that amusing.
Text.LocalizedString: The lighting in this place is far too dim. I asked the owner to brighten it up a bit for Princess Miranjani, but he just laughed it off.//I didn't find that amusing.

Text.SourceString: This town is different from what I'm used to underwater. It's louder, busier... I need to stay alert for the princess's safety.
Text.LocalizedString: This town is different from what I'm used to underwater. It's louder, busier... I need to stay alert for the princess's safety.

Text.SourceString: Oh, hey there! No farming today?
Text.LocalizedString: Oh, hey there! No farming today?

Text.SourceString: Hey! Look who it is!
Text.LocalizedString: Hey! Look who it is!

Text.SourceString: Well, if it isn't the local farmer! What brings you to town today?
Text.LocalizedString: Well, if it isn't the local farmer! What brings you to town today?

Text.SourceString: Surprise to see you here! Skipping the farm work?
Text.LocalizedString: Surprise to see you here! Skipping the farm work?

Text.SourceString: Yeah? Can I help you?
Text.LocalizedString: Yeah? Can I help you?

Text.SourceString: Hmm? Yes?
Text.LocalizedString: Hmm? Yes?

Text.SourceString: These human clothes are not as comfortable as our mer attire, but they serve their purpose on land.//<NPCName>Denali</> seems to adjust quicker than I do.
Text.LocalizedString: These human clothes are not as comfortable as our mer attire, but they serve their purpose on land.//<NPCName>Denali</> seems to adjust quicker than I do.

Text.SourceString: How do people manage to walk in these things?
Text.LocalizedString: How do people manage to walk in these things?

Text.SourceString: Getting around these streets is tougher than navigating coral reefs, which is really saying something.//<portrait=smirk>I've gained a whole new respect for you.
Text.LocalizedString: Getting around these streets is tougher than navigating coral reefs, which is really saying something.//<portrait=smirk>I've gained a whole new respect for you.

Text.SourceString: I've got to keep an eye on every corner here. On land, threats could come from anywhere.
Text.LocalizedString: I've got to keep an eye on every corner here. On land, threats could come from anywhere.

Text.SourceString: We're here for a reason – to ensure the princess's safety. That's our main duty.//<portrait=annoyed>It seems like <NPCName>Denali</> might be forgetting that.
Text.LocalizedString: We're here for a reason – to ensure the princess's safety. That's our main duty.//<portrait=annoyed>It seems like <NPCName>Denali</> might be forgetting that.

Text.SourceString: I can't believe how many different smells and sounds there are on land.//<portrait=smirk>It's overwhelming but...fascinating in its own way.
Text.LocalizedString: I can't believe how many different smells and sounds there are on land.//<portrait=smirk>It's overwhelming but...fascinating in its own way.

Text.SourceString: All these land-dwellers, rushing about. Don't they ever take time to just float and enjoy the moment.
Text.LocalizedString: All these land-dwellers, rushing about. Don't they ever take time to just float and enjoy the moment.

Text.SourceString: The princess seems to enjoy these surface adventures.//It's our job to ensure she can do it safely.
Text.LocalizedString: The princess seems to enjoy these surface adventures.//It's our job to ensure she can do it safely.

Text.SourceString: Hmm... Maybe I should station myself near a human to blend in and keep watch.
Text.LocalizedString: Hmm... Maybe I should station myself near a human to blend in and keep watch.

Text.SourceString: We've just arrived and are settled in at the inn for the week. We're here for the cherry blossom event on the 10th.//Will you be there too?
Text.LocalizedString: We've just arrived and are settled in at the inn for the week. We're here for the cherry blossom event on the 10th.//Will you be there too?

Text.SourceString: I need to secure the area for tomorrow's cherry blossom event.//It's crucial to ensure there's no threat to the princess. I'll handle this tonight.
Text.LocalizedString: I need to secure the area for tomorrow's cherry blossom event.//It's crucial to ensure there's no threat to the princess. I'll handle this tonight.

Text.SourceString: The event yesterday went off without a hitch, and I actually enjoyed myself.
Text.LocalizedString: The event yesterday went off without a hitch, and I actually enjoyed myself.

Text.SourceString: This place isn't so bad, you know...the weather is kind of pleasant here.
Text.LocalizedString: This place isn't so bad, you know...the weather is kind of pleasant here.

Text.SourceString: We'll be heading back in a few days. We can't afford to linger here for too long.
Text.LocalizedString: We'll be heading back in a few days. We can't afford to linger here for too long.

Text.SourceString: I must admit, these Spring colors are impressive.
Text.LocalizedString: I must admit, these Spring colors are impressive.

Text.SourceString: These pants make walking a challenge.
Text.LocalizedString: These pants make walking a challenge.

Text.SourceString: Sometimes I forget I have two separate legs now, instead of just one taill.
Text.LocalizedString: Sometimes I forget I have two separate legs now, instead of just one taill.

Text.SourceString: The longer daylight hours are useful for keeping a better watch over the princess. It's a tactical advantage.
Text.LocalizedString: The longer daylight hours are useful for keeping a better watch over the princess. It's a tactical advantage.

Text.SourceString: I've tried one of these 'coconut drinks' the locals speak of. Refreshing, really helps beat the heat.
Text.LocalizedString: I've tried one of these 'coconut drinks' the locals speak of. Refreshing, really helps beat the heat.

Text.SourceString: The sun here is much more direct than underwater.//<portrait=smirk>It's a different kind of warmth, one that requires getting used to.
Text.LocalizedString: The sun here is much more direct than underwater.//<portrait=smirk>It's a different kind of warmth, one that requires getting used to.

Text.SourceString: I find the concept of 'sunbathing' odd. Lying in the sun for pleasure is an unusual way to enjoy its warmth.
Text.LocalizedString: I find the concept of 'sunbathing' odd. Lying in the sun for pleasure is an unusual way to enjoy its warmth.

Text.SourceString: A nice, cold beer sounds good right about now.
Text.LocalizedString: A nice, cold beer sounds good right about now.

Text.SourceString: A nice glass of wine would be great right now.
Text.LocalizedString: A nice glass of wine would be great right now.

Text.SourceString: I never realized how textured sand really is, since I usually don't touch it when swimming.
Text.LocalizedString: I never realized how textured sand really is, since I usually don't touch it when swimming.

Text.SourceString: Land food is great, but for me, nothing beats a reef burger.
Text.LocalizedString: Land food is great, but for me, nothing beats a reef burger.

Text.SourceString: Cleaning the beach yesterday was fun, though I saw some people fully dressed.//<portrait=annoyed>Can't imagine how hot they must've been.
Text.LocalizedString: Cleaning the beach yesterday was fun, though I saw some people fully dressed.//<portrait=annoyed>Can't imagine how hot they must've been.

Text.SourceString: We're heading back to the kingdom tomorrow morning, first thing.
Text.LocalizedString: We're heading back to the kingdom tomorrow morning, first thing.

Text.SourceString: It's good we're staying close to the beach.//If it gets overwhelming or if anything happens at the beach cleanup, we can evacuate quickly...or just swim back to the kingdom.
Text.LocalizedString: It's good we're staying close to the beach.//If it gets overwhelming or if anything happens at the beach cleanup, we can evacuate quickly...or just swim back to the kingdom.

Text.SourceString: I've been seeing more of you lately. I suppose that's a good thing.
Text.LocalizedString: I've been seeing more of you lately. I suppose that's a good thing.

Text.SourceString: Do you grow any fruits on your farm?
Text.LocalizedString: Do you grow any fruits on your farm?

Text.SourceString: My hair feels huge today. I woke up this morning and bam! It just poofed out.
Text.LocalizedString: My hair feels huge today. I woke up this morning and bam! It just poofed out.

Text.SourceString: Do you grow any fruits on your farm? Will you let me have some?
Text.LocalizedString: Do you grow any fruits on your farm? Will you let me have some?

Text.SourceString: The princess is excited about the Spooky Festival, so here we are.//<portrait=smirk>You'll be there too, right, cutie? It's on the 28th.
Text.LocalizedString: The princess is excited about the Spooky Festival, so here we are.//<portrait=smirk>You'll be there too, right, cutie? It's on the 28th.

Text.SourceString: The princess is keen on attending the Spooky Festival, so that's why we're here.
Text.LocalizedString: The princess is keen on attending the Spooky Festival, so that's why we're here.

Text.SourceString: I need to check the area thoroughly tonight to ensure there's nothing suspicious for tomorrow's event.
Text.LocalizedString: I need to check the area thoroughly tonight to ensure there's nothing suspicious for tomorrow's event.

Text.SourceString: I caught wind of some beachgoers mentioning real ghosts...apparitions, they said, appearing around here.//Is that true? Have you seen any?
Text.LocalizedString: I caught wind of some beachgoers mentioning real ghosts...apparitions, they said, appearing around here.//Is that true? Have you seen any?

Text.SourceString: The leaves changing color remind me of the shifting tides...and for some reason, Poseidon.//<portrait=normal>Anyway, Fall brings a different kind of beauty to the land.
Text.LocalizedString: The leaves changing color remind me of the shifting tides...and for some reason, Poseidon.//<portrait=normal>Anyway, Fall brings a different kind of beauty to the land.

Text.SourceString: Seeing the land-dwellers prepare for the colder months is interesting...wearing scarves, big shoes.//It's a different kind of survival than under the sea.
Text.LocalizedString: Seeing the land-dwellers prepare for the colder months is interesting...wearing scarves, big shoes.//It's a different kind of survival than under the sea.

Text.SourceString: The shorter days make night patrols more frequent. It’s a good exercise in vigilance.
Text.LocalizedString: The shorter days make night patrols more frequent. It’s a good exercise in vigilance.

Text.SourceString: With the days getting shorter, we're doing more patrols at night.//Keeps us on our toes, and the snow really tests our stamina.
Text.LocalizedString: With the days getting shorter, we're doing more patrols at night.//Keeps us on our toes, and the snow really tests our stamina.

Text.SourceString: This time, the beach has a different feel. Less crowded, more serene.
Text.LocalizedString: This time, the beach has a different feel. Less crowded, more serene.

Text.SourceString: Tomorrow's the last day of this year. Think a midnight kiss is in order?
Text.LocalizedString: Tomorrow's the last day of this year. Think a midnight kiss is in order?

Text.SourceString: Tomorrow's the last day of the year. You all set for it?
Text.LocalizedString: Tomorrow's the last day of the year. You all set for it?

Text.SourceString: Am I dressed right for the season?
Text.LocalizedString: Am I dressed right for the season?

Text.SourceString: Walking in snow is tough. Someone really should clear it.
Text.LocalizedString: Walking in snow is tough. Someone really should clear it.

Text.SourceString: Land dwellers make a big deal out of the year's end. Underwater, it's just another day.
Text.LocalizedString: Land dwellers make a big deal out of the year's end. Underwater, it's just another day.

Text.SourceString: It's a bit cold today, isn't it?
Text.LocalizedString: It's a bit cold today, isn't it?

Text.SourceString: Can you actually farm in this weather?//I can't imagine planting anything with the soil as hard as rock like it is now.
Text.LocalizedString: Can you actually farm in this weather?//I can't imagine planting anything with the soil as hard as rock like it is now.

Text.SourceString: I'm hoping we can spend a bit of time together now that I'm here.
Text.LocalizedString: I'm hoping we can spend a bit of time together now that I'm here.

Text.SourceString: How about I visit you tonight, maybe? After my shift is over?
Text.LocalizedString: How about I visit you tonight, maybe? After my shift is over?

Text.SourceString: You should let me take you out one of these days.
Text.LocalizedString: You should let me take you out one of these days.
